Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥計  最近有好消息嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然什麼都沒有?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情越來越糟,甚至在Midland的城堡小鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從Griffith當了國王 開始就變得黑暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說話小心點!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定有人在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的女孩 但不要捲進去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰..誰來幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道沒人會救這美麗的女孩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道不認為很可悲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥計
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人給我們留了張桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥計  把喝的拿上來!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 寶貝兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要撒出來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要是你撒了 我會叫你從這桌子上添掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C..Colette
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請..請放了Colett吧 求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了  老頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了  是你們先撞到我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為光道歉就可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會幫你管教這女孩的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 何不給我倒一點?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 到底是撒了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不懂禮貌嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在全舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快舔!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不快點的話  就滲到桌子裡了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別浪費哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別偷懶!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是不是很不錯啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  可別剩下了哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子弄乾淨 直到能看到你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我們是誰嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會叫你付出代價的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要見你的主子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這消息帶給你們主子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣劍客來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑..黑衣劍客?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙弄得一團糟!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑劍客?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他全身穿著黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著一把比他還大的巨劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且會使用十字連射弩作戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在幾秒內就把城堡的守衛幹掉!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼呢  大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地搜索他 可別有遺漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要找到他!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼向主人解釋呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個全身穿著黑衣的男人!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  原來這就是這鎮子所發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大臣帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣劍客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又是他們!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體是屬於我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是無法擺脫我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的血..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的肉和骨頭..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我們的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那印記...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那印記...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那印記...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你有這印記,你的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至你的恐懼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了  Fief閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在是大臣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大臣 由於你不告訴我這些事 我感到你很不信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死這些人的只是個流浪漢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他是黑衣劍客 難道不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會給你更多的食物和錢作為補償
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我們也會抓住那個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以..拜託...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來很累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 你要擔心的是自己的性命 不是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的食物...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金錢...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這些沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想好好歡迎下這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡聽人們在火中掙扎的呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那骨頭碎裂的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很樂意為他準備個這樣的典禮!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保證過不會對我的人民做出任何事的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎對你的人民...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺光所有的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒光所有的東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這..這裡發生了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大臣!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的盡頭了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連馬都劈成兩半!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人類怎麼能使用這樣的劍?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說過你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個給我們Servant 帶來麻煩的黑衣劍客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 只不過是個人類  不要把我們看扁了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Behelit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這凡人是殺不死我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人類能殺死我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪..怪物!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能動?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是普通人的話 剛才那下就應該幹掉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是多麼的脆弱!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結局!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是很脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好品嚐吃掉你的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將成為我的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說人類是不能殺死你的  是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..那個印記!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人類是很脆弱而且平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使我們受傷或是受到折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們依然要生存
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會感覺到和我們的一樣的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當人們對你說這話的時候 你是怎麼做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小子  你真的要同我對戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠膽量  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我用斧子把你的頭砍下來的時候!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了什麼來到這世上的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了什麼生存著的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了什麼會注定遇見對他們重要的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事都各自遵循著命運
